def my_func(input1:str, input2:str):
    if not (1 <= len(input1) <= 20 and 1 <= len(input2) <= 20):
        return []
    result = []
    length = len(input2)
    index = input1.find(input2)
    while index != -1:
        result.append(index)
        index = input1.find(input2, index + length)
    return result
